⌊\frac ab⌋
a = be+r
r<b
e\in\Bbb Z
 be\le a = be+r<be+b = (e+1)b;\\ e\le \frac ab< e+1 
 e = [\frac ab] 
\begin{eqnarray}{\bf Hint}\  &&0 \le a-be\, <\, b\\  \iff &&  0 \le a/b-e < 1\\ \iff &&   e  \le a/b < e+1\\ \iff &&   e =\lfloor a/b\rfloor \end{eqnarray}
